title: Douglas Adams - Dirk Gently and Hitchhiker
description:
Collection of Douglas Adams' novels, comprising:

Dirk Gently's Series

1 - Dirk Gently's Holistic Detective Agency
2 - The Long Dark Tea-Time of the Soul

Hitchhiker's Trilogy

1 - The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy
2 - The Restaurant at the End of the Universe
3 - Life, the Universe, and Everything
4 - So Long, and Thanks for All the Fish
5 - Mostly Harmless
* - Young Zaphod Plays it Safe

They are all LaTeX-typeset pdfs. The .tex files are included.
